    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/1d469b083c7209068f2d89a8cadde2ef.avif?t=1726781405\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/12e13002d0d40bfa001218d699164c61.avif?t=1726781405\" width=650 height=100 /></span><br><strong>INSPECTION REPORT</strong> is a horror / point &amp; click game focused on exploration and dialogue. Fulfill your duties as a building inspector and explore an abandoned property three years after a catastrophic event ravaged it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/4f41a941919f037c44822a77fe51a102.poster.avif?t=1726781405\" width=450 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/4f41a941919f037c44822a77fe51a102.webm?t=1726781405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/4f41a941919f037c44822a77fe51a102.mp4?t=1726781405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Set in a desolate city, use your flashlight to explore one of your employer's branches. Discover the secrets of the building while avoiding its dangers. Having three separate timelines to go from, connect all the dots in the story and assemble the truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/fd7882238de3a380975193034deb85c8.poster.avif?t=1726781405\" width=450 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/fd7882238de3a380975193034deb85c8.webm?t=1726781405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/fd7882238de3a380975193034deb85c8.mp4?t=1726781405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103400/extras/417eac04757811ba188e342ef13f93c1.avif?t=1726781405\" width=650 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Use your flashlight:</strong> Navigate totally in the dark with only a fraction of your screen visible. Things may or may not attack you out of sight.<br></li><li><strong>Uncover items:</strong> Use them in clever ways to advance further, or to defend yourself.<br></li><li><strong>Discover and explore rooms:</strong> Analyze the signs and clues that remain hidden in the building.<br></li><li><strong>Solve puzzles:</strong> Work through passwords and rituals to progress in the narrative.<br></li><li><strong>Stay out of harm's way:</strong> Hide or suffer the consequences.<br></li><li><strong>Speak with the characters:</strong> You are not alone. Are they who they really say the are?</li></ul>",
